## Technologies Used

- **Framework**: Next.js 14 (App Router), React 18
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS, tailwindcss-animate
- **UI Components**: shadcn/ui (Radix primitives), Chakra UI, Ark UI
- **Icons**: lucide-react, @heroicons/react, Geist font
- **Theming**: next-themes (dark/light)
- **State/Context**: React Context, hooks
- **Authentication**: Firebase Auth
- **Database**: Firebase Firestore + Realtime Database
- **Editor**: Monaco Editor (@monaco-editor/react)
- **AI/LLM**: LangChain, Google Generative AI SDK, LangGraph
- **Networking**: Axios
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Notifications**: react-hot-toast, sonner, react-toastify
- **Email/Comms**: Nodemailer, EmailJS
- **3D/Graphics**: OGL, Spline

